cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM

The paper discusses a deep learning model for content-based image retrieval using natural language processing. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Finally, since the paper deals with images and videos, it may also fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
